  "profileBadgeCrystalsTitle": "Crystals ✦",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsLead": "Crystals are your posts that survived 24 hours and earned genuine engagement, turning from a fleeting moment into a lasting mark.",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsStep1": "Post something worth discussing — a moment, an image, or an idea.",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsStep2": "Every interaction (like, reply) increases the post's gravity.",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsStep3": "Reach the crystallization threshold before the 24 hours end → it becomes a permanent ✦ saved in your crystals.",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsStep4": "Posts without engagement quietly disappear after 24 hours (that's what makes a crystal valuable).",
  "profileBadgeCrystalsTip": "Crystals appear to visitors on your profile as proof of your mark. Share what lasts, not what piles up.",
  "profileBadgeStreakTitle": "Streak 🔥",
  "profileBadgeStreakLead": "The streak is your run of consecutive days on Sarhny. Every day you post adds a spark to your flame.",
  "profileBadgeStreakStep1": "Open the app and post at least once every 24 hours.",
  "profileBadgeStreakStep2": "The streak keeps your run alive for up to 48 hours as a breathing margin.",
  "profileBadgeStreakStep3": "The longer the streak, the nobler and more prominent your glow becomes on your profile.",
  "profileBadgeStreakStep4": "Breaking the streak resets the counter — but it doesn't erase the crystals you've built.",
  "profileBadgeStreakTip": "The streak measures dedication, not quality. A little every day beats a lot in one day.",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsTitle": "Mirrors 🪞",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsLead": "A mirror is an open question you ask, letting people describe you honestly through it. Answers accumulate into a cloud that reflects how those around you see you.",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsStep1": "Tap the “Mirrors” tab and create a reflective question (e.g. What stands out most about me?).",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsStep2": "Share the mirror link with your friends or on your account in another app.",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsStep3": "Answers arrive anonymously — you don't know who said what, so people speak frankly.",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsStep4": "Each mirror earns you a 🪞 badge that shows on your profile and boosts your weight on Sarhny.",
  "profileBadgeMirrorsTip": "Mirrors work best with specific questions, not vague ones. Ask about what you really want to know.",
